所有程序包的分层结构

程序包分层结构:
  • dao,
  • entity,
  • service,
  • serviceImpl,
  • util

类分层结构

  • java.lang.Object
    • entity.BorrowRecord
    • serviceImpl.BorrowRecordServiceImpl (implements service.BorrowRecordService)
    • util.DButil
    • entity.Device
    • serviceImpl.DeviceServiceImpl (implements service.DeviceService)
    • serviceImpl.FixedRecordServiceImpl (implements service.MaintenanceRecordService)
    • entity.MaintenanceRecord
    • entity.User
    • serviceImpl.UserServiceImpl (implements service.UserService)

接口分层结构

  • dao.BorrowRecordDAO
  • service.BorrowRecordService
  • dao.DeviceDAO
  • service.DeviceService
  • dao.FixedRecordDAO
  • service.MaintenanceRecordService
  • dao.UserDAO
  • service.UserService
